Inside my single story home. I was sitting in my bedroom floor. The house is wood frame with brick around it, halfway up. The bricks going around it have cracks in them and have separated from the house in some places. Our concrete porch was cracked and had moved. Two others with me inside also felt this and were scared. We all went outside. There were two people outside, in the yard. They also felt it.
